Subdirectories:
---------------

util       utility classes for scientific computation (namespace Util)
simp       general classes for simpatico simulations (namespace Simp)
mcMd       serial Monte Carlo (MC) / molecular dynamics (MD) (namespace McMd)
ddMd       parallel domain-decomposition MD simulation (namespace DdMd)
mdPp       pre- and postprocessing tools (namespace MdPp)
test       unit test framework
draft      unfinished or proposed classes

Note: The contents of directories util/ and test/ are maintained in separate 
git repositories on github.com, and are included in simpatico as git submodules.
The directories will be populated if the simpatico directory is compiled using
the -recursive option, but will initially be empty if simpatico is cloned 
without this option.

Files (before running the setup script):
----------------------------------------

makefile      main makefile for in-source builds
configure     configure script (for en|dis-abling compile time options)
programs.mod  doxygen module for documentation of complete programs
CONTENTS      this file

Setup and configuration:
------------------------

For compilation instructions, see the README file in the root directory (the 
parent of this directory) and the web documentation in doc/html.
